<script>
    // copy
    function copy_text(text){
        try {
            navigator.clipboard.writeText(text).then(()=>alert(text + ' copied!'));
        } catch (err) {
            alert(text);
        }
    }
    const root = document.getElementById('main').attachShadow({mode: 'open'});
    root.innerHTML=document.getElementById('main').innerHTML;

</script>
